data.description: This home is a must see!  Large 4 bed, 2.5 bath home for under $275k!  Spacious, modern, open concept, main level living space with large living room and dining room open to the kitchen.  Kitchen has plenty of cabinet and countertop space with a large island and a pantry.  The island with sink overlooks the spacious living and dining rooms.  There is also a main level half bath for your guests.  The second floor boasts a loft are, large owners suite with a garden tub, walk-in shower and an ample walk-in closet.  There are also 3 additional bedrooms and another full bathroom on the second level.  The home has a smart home system (lighting, door lock and garage door controls) with an alarm system and cameras built in. This is a corner lot with sizeable fenced backyard.
